---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate disclosure"
  description="How Last Thread Co. makes money, and what that means for you."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-olive">Disclosure</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 font-serif text-4xl text-ink sm:text-5xl">
      How we pay for the lights.
    </h1>

    <div class="prose-lt mt-10 space-y-6 text-ink/90">
      <p>
        Last Thread Co. is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC
        Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to
        provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and
        linking to Amazon.com. We may also participate in other affiliate
        programs from time to time.
      </p>
      <p>
        In plain English: when you click a product link on this site and end
        up buying something, we get a small commission from the retailer. It
        doesn't change the price you pay. It's how a site like this one
        stays free to read, and how we cover the cost of writing, photography,
        and the very modest server bill.
      </p>
      <p>
        A few things we promise about how we use those links. First, we
        don't get paid to feature products, ever. No brand pays us to include
        them in a guide, and no PR rep can talk their way onto the site by
        sending us a sample. Second, we don't link to something we wouldn't
        recommend to our own family. If it isn't good enough to give to your
        dad, it isn't good enough for the site. Third, when we get something
        wrong — and we will, sooner or later — we'll update the page and
        leave a note about what changed.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you ever feel like we recommended something that wasn't worth it,
        we'd genuinely like to hear about it. The whole point of the project
        is to be a trustworthy short list, not a long one.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-lt p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-ink);
  }
</style>
